  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, you can empower yourself with the legends &mdash; whether true or exaggerated &mdash; of your great deeds. As a bonus action, you gain the following benefits for 1 minute:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You are blessed with an otherworldly presence, gaining advantage on all Charisma checks.</li>\n<li>Once on each of your turns when you make a weapon attack and miss, you can cause that attack to hit instead.</li>\n<li>If you fail a saving throw, you can use your reaction to reroll it. You must use this new roll.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you use this bonus action, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p>",
